- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the behavior of the agents in the population protocol can be seen as a type of distributed computation, which is a topic of interest in neural and evolutionary computing. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper involves designing and analyzing a discrete algorithm for leader election, which involves concepts from discrete mathematics.
